cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper deals with modeling sensor uncertainty in computer vision and robotics, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The use of Bayesian inference techniques and machine learning also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the focus on state estimation and localization suggests that it could also belong to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category.
